data.description: Set on a quiet street in the sought after, Rock Creek neighborhood, this gorgeous property offers designer upgrades & comfortable main level living. Upon entering, the sun drenched living room's soaring ceilings & big windows create a warm ambiance. Eye-catching hickory flooring extends throughout the home. Sophisticated updates in the recently renovated kitchen. Quartz countertops, updated appliances, an abundance of storage in the prep island are highlighted. Open floor plan guides you to an inviting living room with gas fireplace. Upstairs, a secluded primary suite features a 5 piece bath with soaking tub. Three upstairs secondary bedrooms are spacious & bright. Additional large bedroom on the lower level would make ideal guest quarters. Rec room on the lower level makes the perfect family gathering space. Spend quiet afternoons on the deck in the sunny backyard. Mature trees provide shade and privacy. Designed to perfection, this home is ideal for entertainment and relaxation for all buyers looking to experience the Colorado lifestyle.
